Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,【OP】
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.15,0:00:22.65,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,清风　云彩　仰望群星
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.65,0:00:30.96,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,胸中的悸动　如波涛汹涌
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.96,0:00:38.61,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无穷　无尽　战火连绵
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.61,0:00:46.18,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,汝等扬帆　即日踏上征途
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.18,0:00:53.56,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪怕有暗阎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.15,0:01:01.87,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阻塞前行之路
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.41,0:01:13.41,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遥想　祈福　唯愿君平安
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.81,0:01:28.16,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fsp0}向无尽宇宙{\fsp-9}、{\fsp1.5}出征
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,【ED】
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.72,0:23:07.99,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无重力的暗阎　唯有摸索前行
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.31,0:23:10.78,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMS Gothic}Where do we go?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.63,0:23:19.36,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如同莫比乌斯环一般　命运九转轮回
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.36,0:23:22.22,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMS Gothic\fsp0.1}Win, Lose Or Draw
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.07,0:23:28.16,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真实究竟何在{\fnMS Gothic}？ {\fsp0}Lies & Truth
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.52,0:23:34.43,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,光影回转{\fsp-9}　{\fsp1.5}阴阳相生
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.43,0:23:39.39,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,命运之骰一经掷出　就已无法停止转动
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.63,0:23:42.35,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMS Gothic\fsp0}Dive into the Light
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.20,0:23:50.79,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,毁灭之风扬　我只欲逆风直上
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.79,0:23:53.69,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,将你紧紧拥入怀抱中
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.10,0:24:01.80,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,制裁之剑{\fsp-9}　{\fsp1.5}斩断这一昏暗的时代
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.80,0:24:08.24,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,独彷徨　{\fnMS Gothic\fsp0}Lost In Space
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,【Main】
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.72,0:01:39.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哲力胥卿率领舰队在巴格休现身
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.12,0:01:41.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在其炮火之下
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.19,0:01:47.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,留在沙面上的正直老人号为红莲烈火所裹
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.58,0:01:51.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,迎来了其生涯的终点
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.30,0:02:02.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,确信己方获胜的哲力胥卿准备攻入沙漠洞窟
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.94,0:02:09.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,方修利提督也在思索迎敌之策
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.90,0:02:25.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(1443,885)\fad(500,500)\fs90\bord4}热沙的激斗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.69,0:02:31.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大致就是这样
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.64,0:02:34.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个作战很靠运气
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.42,0:02:36.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,风险也很大
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.64,0:02:40.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要不要执行 由大家决定
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.03,0:02:47.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要干
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.65,0:02:51.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,米兰达 舰长…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.97,0:02:54.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们是认真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.57,0:02:58.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那些家伙是正直老人号的仇人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.01,0:03:01.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,此仇不报
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.66,0:03:02.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们咽不下这口气
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.80,0:03:11.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 请两位跟我来
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.70,0:03:13.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就拜托雪拉带路
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.36,0:03:15.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(1343,923)\fad(500,500)}雪拉芬·库帕斯
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.36,0:03:15.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(1343,993)\fad(500,500)\fs62\fnms gothic}セラフィン・クーパーズ
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.52,0:03:15.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,包在我身上
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.92,0:03:20.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,各位 一定不要勉强啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.31,0:03:22.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你才是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.44,0:03:28.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们还没老到夫妻双双归西呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.71,0:03:29.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呐 船长
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.43,0:03:35.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,船长也还年轻着呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.18,0:03:40.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,毕竟他这把年纪还娶了米兰达这种人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.80,0:03:44.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦？你什么意思？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.94,0:03:48.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 没什么 没什么
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.49,0:03:56.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我对你们的勇气表示敬意
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.58,0:04:00.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但要实行作战 需要另一个要素
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.43,0:04:01.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不必多心
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.58,0:04:04.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已经派船去接了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.27,0:04:11.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看来已经来了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.77,0:04:30.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,巴格休正规军居然会靠海贼带路
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.27,0:04:34.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(546,923)\fad(500,500)}托比尔少将
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.27,0:04:34.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(546,993)\fad(500,500)\fs62\fnms gothic}トゥルビル少将
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.75,0:04:34.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是他们通知了敌舰队抵达的消息
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.15,0:04:36.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样应该没问题
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.73,0:04:49.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下来就交给我们了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.87,0:04:52.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打开通信回路
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.77,0:04:55.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要求与哲力胥公直接对话
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.40,0:04:57.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,前方出现巴格休正规军
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.58,0:05:04.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,巴格休政府真要和我们开战吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.62,0:05:06.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,受不了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.78,0:05:10.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没必要为区区面子捋虎须吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.15,0:05:16.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阁下 巴格休舰队指挥官来电
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.49,0:05:18.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接过来
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.38,0:05:22.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,初次见面
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.62,0:05:26.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小官是巴格休政府军 托比尔少将
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.53,0:05:30.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是哲力胥·泰坦尼亚
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.77,0:05:31.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么事
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.23,0:05:34.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们巴格休是独立国家
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.12,0:05:38.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请停止侵犯我国主权的军事活动
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.60,0:05:40.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,马上撤退
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.20,0:05:43.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我无意与巴格休为敌
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.16,0:05:46.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,贵国只需作壁上观
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.28,0:05:52.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,巴格休政府与泰坦尼亚世代交好
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.01,0:05:55.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,万望您能谅解
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.46,0:05:58.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我倒想请你谅解
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.82,0:06:04.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们的目的仅在于捕捉扰乱宇宙秩序的公敌
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.96,0:06:09.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,泰坦尼亚的所作所为才扰乱了我国的秩序
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.38,0:06:14.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看来没有交涉的余地了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.46,0:06:15.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.81,0:06:19.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阁下 这样好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.36,0:06:21.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,若在这里交火的话
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.19,0:06:23.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就无法回头了…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.60,0:06:24.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少啰嗦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.67,0:06:27.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,威吓射击！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.47,0:06:48.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,开火了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.80,0:06:51.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,马上联系政府
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.67,0:06:56.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看来开始了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.78,0:06:59.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要紧吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.86,0:07:02.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个洞窟不会塌掉吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.01,0:07:03.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谁知道呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.28,0:07:06.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里可是上百万年前的古董
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.97,0:07:09.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,若舰队一并掉下来 我可不保证
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.46,0:07:17.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,巴格休军没有撤退的意思
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.10,0:07:23.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也真能忍 但到此为止了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.60,0:07:25.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用管什么巴格休军
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.04,0:07:29.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们是群只会躲在远处抗议的胆小鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.34,0:07:32.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,派突击部队上陆
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.47,0:07:33.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阁下
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.47,0:07:40.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请您将部队指挥权交给我——道尔曼
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.53,0:07:48.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(540,923)\fad(500,500)}道尔曼
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.53,0:07:48.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(540,993)\fad(500,500)\fs62\fnms gothic}ドールマン
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.63,0:07:44.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就凭你？海贼出身的家伙凭什么这样说
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.22,0:07:48.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我很了解方修利的为人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.30,0:07:51.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在捕获方修利一事上比任何人都适任
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.13,0:07:57.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就这么想建功立业吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.72,0:08:00.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吧 就交给你
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.31,0:08:03.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下官一定不辱使命
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.00,0:08:20.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,泰坦尼亚军开始空降了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.15,0:08:23.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,估计要展开地面部队
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.97,0:08:30.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看来自以为强大之人都喜欢以身试法呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.21,0:08:33.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没办法
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.58,0:08:35.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作为一个巴格休军人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.22,0:08:38.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我没法对此视而不见
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.92,0:08:41.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在起 和泰坦尼亚开战
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.50,0:08:44.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 提督…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.80,0:08:49.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,泰坦尼亚没有直接攻击我军
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.17,0:08:54.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,若先发制人的话 我方要为主动开战负责的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.77,0:09:00.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道 伊克少佐 可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.01,0:09:16.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,驱逐舰列凡特被击沉了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.28,0:09:20.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它在试图阻止泰坦尼亚军空降时遭到了攻击
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.91,0:09:25.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样一来就不用负责任了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.00,0:09:27.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反击
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.30,0:09:30.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全舰一齐攻击
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.70,0:09:41.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,开始了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.58,0:09:43.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快点
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.44,0:09:50.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,巴格休舰队开始攻击了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.51,0:09:52.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反击
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.54,0:10:02.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,渚士朗卿 紧急通信
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.61,0:10:08.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哲力胥舰队和巴格休军进入了交战状态
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.22,0:10:13.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然变成这样了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.98,0:10:21.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哲力胥卿不会把一介边境行星的主权放在眼里
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.19,0:10:27.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,法尔密卿刚上任就要忙起来了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.21,0:10:29.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让船快点
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.64,0:10:31.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.07,0:10:49.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,地面部队去捉拿方修利
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.41,0:10:54.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本队随我从正面消灭这些不知天高地厚的家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.08,0:10:59.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,纳西利卡准将率部上升断敌退路
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.79,0:11:00.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.45,0:11:04.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,维希塔准将去攻敌左翼
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.28,0:11:04.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.15,0:11:15.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敌舰队兵分三路 企图包围我军
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.46,0:11:17.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然有些老套
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.83,0:11:21.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但我方势微 这一手段最为有效
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.84,0:11:23.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我方有160艘
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.06,0:11:26.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,泰坦尼亚有220艘以上
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.60,0:11:28.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.70,0:11:32.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只能采取常规战法
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.02,0:11:34.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,且战且退
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.17,0:11:48.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我方节节推进
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.28,0:11:52.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但巴格休军巧妙地后撤
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.37,0:11:53.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我方无机可乘
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.28,0:11:58.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就给对方施加更大的压力
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.91,0:12:00.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本队极速前进
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.27,0:12:02.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,降低高度
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.31,0:12:04.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对巴格休军来个上下夹击
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.50,0:12:23.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,赌场库伦巴 现在开店
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.25,0:12:26.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,收到 随时待命
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.77,0:12:29.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,泰坦尼亚的地面部队似乎还没注意到
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.88,0:12:30.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.89,0:12:35.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.01,0:12:39.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敌人似乎冲着巴格休军开始下降了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.63,0:12:42.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打开开关 一切就绪
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.94,0:12:49.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来了 来了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.42,0:12:56.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给我上 一刀插进对方的咽喉要塞
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.45,0:13:09.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还差一点 还差一点
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.92,0:13:18.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还差一点点 别急
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.54,0:13:26.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有约一分钟完成包围
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.64,0:13:29.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 准备射击
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.33,0:13:31.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,提督
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.21,0:13:34.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 就是现在
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.63,0:13:37.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最后的工作来了 正直老人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.40,0:13:59.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.13,0:14:01.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,机关室受损
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.83,0:14:02.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.04,0:14:04.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阁下 看那里
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.31,0:14:11.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶 怎么会这样
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.25,0:14:18.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就是所谓穷鼠咬猫
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.93,0:14:37.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里危险 回去了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.30,0:14:41.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下来只要迎击空降部队就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.89,0:14:42.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜托了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.07,0:14:45.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说什么呢 你也要战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.47,0:14:48.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然是这样？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.97,0:14:53.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,主引擎失控
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.84,0:14:55.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样下去的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.04,0:15:00.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抬起舰首 准备迫降
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.25,0:15:18.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.08,0:15:21.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阁下 您受伤了吗…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.03,0:15:24.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要紧 擦伤罢了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.42,0:15:26.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全员弃舰
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.98,0:15:31.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,振作点
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.59,0:15:41.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阁下
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.87,0:15:42.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您没事就好
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.68,0:15:44.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,通告僚舰
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.39,0:15:47.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哲力胥阁下仍健在
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.08,0:15:49.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哲力胥阁下仍健在
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.94,0:15:54.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快弃舰 会爆炸的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.79,0:15:59.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哲力胥大人 您没事就好
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.53,0:16:01.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请上车
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.91,0:16:03.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敌旗舰「台风」坠毁
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.38,0:16:05.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在正是好机会
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.22,0:16:08.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,前进击溃敌方舰队！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.52,0:16:10.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阁下
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.66,0:16:13.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,若被认为我方和反泰坦尼亚派串通
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.31,0:16:14.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,日后对我方不利
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.56,0:16:17.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请停止攻击
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.48,0:16:19.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,胆小鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.70,0:16:24.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,事到如今还怕什么
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.88,0:16:26.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给我打 给我打！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.20,0:16:47.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还没干掉2时方向的巡航舰吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.73,0:16:50.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让主炮集中火力狠狠地打
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.16,0:16:56.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蠢货 泰坦尼亚的走狗不足为惧！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.96,0:16:59.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这才是这个人的本性吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.21,0:17:07.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然这样 一不做二不休
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.35,0:17:09.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给我打
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.66,0:17:12.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要放走一匹泰坦尼亚狗！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.40,0:17:21.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,搞什么呢 一群没用的家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.64,0:17:26.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这种时候才要发挥武人的真正价值呢！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.18,0:17:29.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,洞窟入口在那边
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.11,0:17:33.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叛乱军已经开始败退了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.54,0:17:34.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.00,0:17:36.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,古拉尼特 拿枪来
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.58,0:17:38.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是 在此
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.43,0:17:41.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还差一点就要分出胜负了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.13,0:17:45.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一定要亲手抓住方修利
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.72,0:17:56.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第三哨所 发现敌兵
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.39,0:17:59.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第一中队就此撤离
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.39,0:18:01.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把他们引进来
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.26,0:18:07.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样东躲西藏好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.19,0:18:10.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,洞窟再大 终归有个尽头吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.18,0:18:12.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那当然
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.55,0:18:15.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你想说这里连着地狱深处吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.07,0:18:20.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唔 倒也不是不可能…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.90,0:18:27.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好险好险
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.39,0:18:29.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要当心啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.79,0:18:32.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说什么风凉话呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.02,0:18:34.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要在前面迎击了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.65,0:18:44.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,随我来 把鼠辈们尽数杀了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.84,0:19:01.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你以为这样就能阻止我吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.81,0:19:04.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.41,0:19:09.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,捉住方修利之人 可以随意领赏
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.43,0:19:23.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呼吸…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.75,0:19:26.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.89,0:19:28.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阁下 不对劲
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.30,0:19:30.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还请暂且退下
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.15,0:19:33.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,闭嘴
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.08,0:19:37.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶的方修利肯定就在那里
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.69,0:19:44.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那些家伙怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.96,0:19:45.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hypoxia
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.81,0:19:47.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是缺氧症状
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.31,0:19:54.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在那片洼地底部积有高浓度二氧化碳
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.52,0:19:58.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在密闭洞窟里并不稀奇
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.53,0:20:00.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来如此
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.85,0:20:03.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所谓巨龙的盲肠吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.86,0:20:09.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真没想到 哲力胥·泰坦尼亚居然上了钩
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.04,0:20:13.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下来要绝地大反击了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.85,0:20:19.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阁下…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.12,0:20:22.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,古拉尼特…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.40,0:20:31.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.75,0:20:36.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 把哲力胥拿下
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.64,0:20:38.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他有做人质的价值
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.58,0:20:43.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别小看我
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.52,0:21:14.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这家伙是怪物
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.58,0:21:22.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,荣幸吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.95,0:21:28.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,泰坦尼亚的公爵会和你这种下贱之辈亲自过招
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.30,0:21:31.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可不想和你对战
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.47,0:21:36.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给我识相点 下贱之辈
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.79,0:21:45.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在哪里 方修利在哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.84,0:21:53.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快说 还是说你想死吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.76,0:21:54.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.64,0:22:12.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快回答 方修利在哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.13,0:22:15.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你自己找去
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.30,0:22:19.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么 不准顶嘴
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.26,0:22:21.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,区区鼠辈！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.78,0:22:23.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不许动 哲力胥！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.75,0:22:32.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放下石头 乖乖举起手来
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.04,0:24:20.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哲力胥军和方修利一派开始了最终决战
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.13,0:24:24.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,若能顺利生擒方修利 凯旋天城的话
Dialogue: 0,0:24:25.30,0:24:27.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就能打上圆满的休止符了
Dialogue: 0,0:24:24.97,0:24:30.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(695,338)\fad(500,0)\fs90\bord5}终幕的镇魂歌


